<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#E5C07B;">3.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;"> Zou, Z., Bai, R., Li, X., Xu, B., Chen, L., Liu, C., &amp; Hao, M. (2024). &quot;Thermal rectification induced by phonon hydrodynamics in asymmetric 2D microstructures.&quot; Materials Today Physics, 40, 101319.</span></span>
