<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#E5C07B;">6.</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;"> Li, J., &amp; Yang, L. (2023). &quot;Recent Development of Heat Sink and Related Design Methods.&quot; Energies, 16(20), 7133. (Review covering natural/forced convection, microchannels, TPMS, bionic designs.)</span></span>
